Parliament, Monday, 26 August 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Women, Youth and Persons with Disabilities, will be briefed by the National Youth Development Agency (NYDA) on its annual performance plan (APP) for 2019/20. Details of the meetings: Date : Tuesday, 27 August 2019
	Time : 10:30-16:00
	Venue : Committee Room V227, Second Floor, Old Assembly Building Meanwhile, the Portfolio Committee on Social Development will have a joint meeting with the Select Committee on Health and Social Services. The committee will receive a presentation from the Department of Social Development on the facilitation of the recruitment process on the appointment of candidates to serve on the Central Drug Authority (CDA) board. In addition, the committee will adopt the programme for the interviews of candidates to serve in the CDA Board. Details of the meeting Date : Tuesday, 27 August 2019
	Time : 10:00-13:00
	Venue : Committee Room M315, Third Floor, Marks Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8203 
	Cell: 081 497 4694
